.TH "SFTPGO-GEN-COMPLETION-FISH" "1" "Mar 2026" "SFTPGo 2.7.99-dev" "SFTPGo Manual"

.SH NAME
sftpgo-gen-completion-fish - Generate the autocompletion script for fish


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBsftpgo gen completion fish\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Generate the autocompletion script for the fish shell.

.PP
To load completions in your current shell session:

.PP
$ sftpgo gen completion fish | source

.PP
To load completions for every new session, execute once:

.PP
$ sftpgo gen completion fish > ~/.config/fish/completions/sftpgo.fish

.PP
You will need to start a new shell for this setup to take effect.


.SH OPTIONS
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for fish


.SH SEE ALSO
\fBsftpgo-gen-completion(1)\fP
